intp (0.1.0~placeholder2-1) noble; urgency=low

  * Re-upload after orig tarball regeneration. The previous
    0.1.0~placeholder-1 orig tarball was created with `git archive`
    run from a subdirectory, which (via cwd-relative pathspec
    matching) captured only packaging/debian/* instead of the full
    upstream tree, so Launchpad's meson configure step found no
    meson.build at the source root.
  * No upstream code changes; this is a pure re-roll of the source
    tarball.

